title: Project Skins Release Date
body: The PROJECT skins for First Strike will be released tomorrow for all servers just to make it clear.

replies.body: What time will the skins be coming out tomorrow and do you know if they will be in a bundle or by themselves?
They're coming out around 3:00pm AWST or 5:00pm AEST. I'm pretty sure that they'll be available in both, but I have no inside information so thats just a guess.
Where do you live may i ask? What state?
WA, so it would be 3pm for me
